SUMMARY:Grace & Hope
DESCRIPTION:Grace & Hope is a faith-based recovery support group meeting for those in recovery from alcohol or drug addiction. Grace & Hope is a meeting that shares the message that the God of the Bible is a loving\, caring\, and compassionate God and he wants to help you be successful in recovery and even over any struggle of life.\nGrace & Hope is held every Tuesday evening from 7:00-8:00pm at Calvary Church.\nRegistration is not required.\nContact Email: graceandhope@calvarychurch.org\nPhone Contact: Pastoral Care Team at (717) 509-6242 x278
URL:https://www.calvarychurch.org/calendar/grace-and-hope-27/
CATEGORIES:Pastoral Care,Website Calendar
END:VEVENT
